11#include "ipf.h"
12
13
14u_32_t optname(cp, sp, linenum)
15 char ***cp;
16 u_short *sp;
17 int linenum;
18{
19 struct ipopt_names *io, *so;
20 u_long msk = 0;
21 u_short smsk = 0;
22 char *s;
23 int sec = 0;
24
25 for (s = strtok(**cp, ","); s; s = strtok(NULL, ",")) {
26 for (io = ionames; io->on_name; io++)
27 if (!strcasecmp(s, io->on_name)) {
28 msk |= io->on_bit;
29 break;
30 }
31 if (!io->on_name) {
32 fprintf(stderr, "%d: unknown IP option name %s\n",
33 linenum, s);
34 return 0;
35 }
36 if (!strcasecmp(s, "sec-class"))
37 sec = 1;
38 }
39
40 if (sec && !*(*cp + 1)) {
41 fprintf(stderr, "%d: missing security level after sec-class\n",
42 linenum);
43 return 0;
44 }
45
46 if (sec) {
47 (*cp)++;
48 for (s = strtok(**cp, ","); s; s = strtok(NULL, ",")) {
49 for (so = secclass; so->on_name; so++)
50 if (!strcasecmp(s, so->on_name)) {
51 smsk |= so->on_bit;
52 break;
53 }
54 if (!so->on_name) {
55 fprintf(stderr,
56 "%d: no such security level: %s\n",
57 linenum, s);
58 return 0;
59 }
60 }
61 if (smsk)
62 *sp = smsk;
63 }
64 return msk;
65}
